│ 2042 public:                                                                                                                                │
│ 2043   /// The blend operation is a User of the incoming values and of their                                                                │
│ 2044   /// respective masks, ordered [I0, M0, I1, M1, I2, M2, ...]. Note that M0 can                                                        │
